REM Title: Show public IP + geo
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Curls ifconfig.co for the egress IP plus city/country guess.
REM Useful sanity check after VPN toggles.
REM Target: macOS
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING curl -s ifconfig.co/json | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null || curl -s ifconfig.me
ENTER
